      <title>俄罗斯央行从2026年起削减外汇销售，取消对卢布的部分支持</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-central-bank-cuts-own-forex-sales-2026-withdrawing-some-support-rouble-2025-12-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯央行周五表示，将从新年起将外汇干预措施减少一半，预计此举将在 2026 年消除对卢布的部分支撑，经济学家预计卢布将走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-central-bank-cuts-own-forex-sales-2026-withdrawing-some-support-rouble-2025-12-26/</guid>
